.TH trust 1  "trust " 
.SH NAME
trust \- Inspect and delegate local trust
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBtrust\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Inspect and delegate local trust
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
trust\-show(1)
Show trust and moderation state
.TP
trust\-delegate(1)
Delegate trust to a publisher identity
.TP
trust\-provider(1)
Manage provider trust and bans
.TP
trust\-stream(1)
Publish or subscribe to provider trust signals
.TP
trust\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
